<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 03:13:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国称与台湾和平“统一”的前景受到“侵蚀”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/prospect-peaceful-reunification-with-taiwan-being-eroded-china-says-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国国防部长董军周日表示，与台湾和平“统一”的前景正日益受到台独分裂分子和外部势力的“侵蚀”，并承诺确保“台独”永远不会发生。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 01:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/prospect-peaceful-reunification-with-taiwan-being-eroded-china-says-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部长泽连斯基主导香格里拉对话最后一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-defence-minister-ukraines-zelenskiy-dominate-shangri-la-dialogues-last-2024-06-02/</link><description>在中国国防部长董军发表讲话的前一天，美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀告诉代表们，印太地区仍然是美国的一个重点关注点。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 00:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-defence-minister-ukraines-zelenskiy-dominate-shangri-la-dialogues-last-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国在历史性样本回收任务中登陆月球背面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-lands-uncrewed-spacecraft-far-side-moon-2024-06-01/</link><description>此次登陆提升了中国在全球登月热潮中的太空强国地位，各国都希望利用月球矿物来维持长期的宇航员任务和月球基地。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 23:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-lands-uncrewed-spacecraft-far-side-moon-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>摩尔多瓦反对派领导人呼吁与俄罗斯和中国建立更好的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovan-opposition-leader-calls-better-ties-with-russia-china-2024-06-01/</link><description>摩尔多瓦最大反对党的亲俄罗斯领导人呼吁改善与俄罗斯和中国的关系，并敦促其他团体联合起来，在十月的选举中选出亲欧洲总统马亚·桑杜的单一挑战者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovan-opposition-leader-calls-better-ties-with-russia-china-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大国防部长表示，加拿大向中国提出了外国干涉的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-raised-foreign-interference-concerns-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-01/</link><description>加拿大国防部长周六表示，在一次罕见的两国国防部长会议上，加拿大警告中国不要干预其选举。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 08:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-raised-foreign-interference-concerns-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示5月份中国新建住宅价格连续第9个月上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-home-prices-inch-up-9th-month-may-survey-shows-2024-06-01/</link><description>一项私人调查显示，中国新房价格在 5 月份连续第九个月小幅上涨，受到一系列支撑中国受危机打击的房地产行业的支持性措施的推动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 02:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-new-home-prices-inch-up-9th-month-may-survey-shows-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国将焦点转向中国风险 泽伦斯基抵达亚洲防务会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-refocuses-attention-china-security-risks-2024-06-01/</link><description>人们越来越担心，华盛顿专注于帮助乌克兰对抗俄罗斯的入侵和支持以色列在加沙的战争，从而转移了印度-太平洋地区的注意力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 01:10:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-refocuses-attention-china-security-risks-2024-06-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国粮食安全法生效 力争绝对自给自足</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-food-security-law-comes-into-force-aims-absolute-self-sufficiency-2024-05-31/</link><description>中国首部旨在实现主粮“绝对自给自足”的粮食安全法于周六生效，加强了全球最大农产品进口国降低对海外采购依赖的努力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 23:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-food-security-law-comes-into-force-aims-absolute-self-sufficiency-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员要求联邦调查局就金斯瑞生物科技与中国的联系提供简报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-ask-fbi-briefing-genscript-biotechs-links-china-2024-05-31/</link><description>美国众议院中国委员会已要求联邦调查局和情报界提供有关金斯瑞生物科技公司及其三家子公司的情况通报，以确定中国共产党是否对其运营施加影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 19:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-lawmakers-ask-fbi-briefing-genscript-biotechs-links-china-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国表示可能因俄罗斯战争支持而对中国企业和银行采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-it-could-act-against-china-firms-banks-over-russian-war-support-2024-05-31/</link><description>拜登政府加强了对中国支持莫斯科的警告。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-it-could-act-against-china-firms-banks-over-russian-war-support-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>西西帕斯轻松击败张晋级法网第四轮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tsitsipas-glides-past-zhang-into-french-open-fourth-round-2024-05-31/</link><description>周五，希腊选手斯特凡诺斯·西西帕斯以6-3 6-3 6-1战胜中国选手张志珍，连续第六年进入法网第四轮。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/tsitsipas-glides-past-zhang-into-french-open-fourth-round-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>戴着牛仔帽的特斯拉董事金巴尔·马斯克是谁？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/who-is-kimbal-musk-tesla-director-cowboy-hat-2024-05-31/</link><description>特斯拉股东将于 6 月 13 日投票批准首席执行官埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 560 亿美元的薪酬方案，该方案于 1 月份被特拉华州法官宣布无效。即将到来的还有董事的连任，其中包括马斯克的弟弟金巴尔。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/who-is-kimbal-musk-tesla-director-cowboy-hat-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>斯瓦泰克和年轻球员轻松获胜，愤怒的卢布廖夫在法国公开赛上摔倒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/easy-swiatek-sinner-raging-rublev-falls-after-french-open-meltdown-2024-05-31/</link><description>周五，在法网又一个潮湿的日子里，伊加·斯瓦泰克保持冷静，轻松进入法网第四轮，但红雾降临在安德烈·鲁布列夫身上，他在成为男子最高种子选手之前大发雷霆并被淘汰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:21:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/easy-swiatek-sinner-raging-rublev-falls-after-french-open-meltdown-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>北京表示，中国外交部副部长敦促美国停止“抹黑”中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-vice-foreign-minister-urged-us-stop-smearing-china-beijing-says-2024-05-31/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国外交部副部长马朝旭本周在华盛顿举行会谈，敦促美国不要“抹黑”中国，停止对中国企业实施“滥用”制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-vice-foreign-minister-urged-us-stop-smearing-china-beijing-says-2024-05-31/</guid></item><item><title>法国、德国敦促欧盟加强对生物燃料进口的欺诈调查检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/france-germany-urge-tougher-eu-checks-biofuel-imports-fraud-probe-2024-05-31/</link><description>随着欧盟调查来自亚洲的进口欺诈指控，法国和德国呼吁欧盟对海外生物燃料供应商采取更严格的检查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/france-germany-urge-tougher-eu-checks-biofuel-imports-fraud-probe-2024-05-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>